  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网遥测流的架构图。核心是从边缘节点采集数据，经过MQTT Broker转发，最后到执行器控制器。我想用一个子图来封装整个遥测流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S33",
        "S33_root",
        "S33_A",
        "S33_B",
        "S33_C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，子图名字叫IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream。里面放四个节点：边缘节点作为入口，两个MQTT Broker做中继，最后到执行器控制器。但为什么需要两个Broker？是主备还是级联？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S33",
        "S33_A",
        "S33_B"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是级联架构。边缘节点先连到边缘侧的Broker，再连到云端Broker，最后到控制器。所以S33_A是边缘MQTT Broker，S33_B是云端MQTT Broker。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S33_root",
        "S33_A",
        "S33_B",
        "S33_C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我设计成链式连接：S33_root → S33_A → S33_B → S33_C。另外，我需要在子图外面放一个虚线框的依赖节点D33，用虚线连到S33_root，表示这是外部依赖的遥测流定义。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D33",
        "S33_root",
        "dep"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "这个设计可以。D33代表遥测流的逻辑定义，S33是具体实现实例。虚线样式很合适。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D33",
        "S33",
        "dep"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了。子图S33包含四个节点，链式连接。D33用虚线边框，通过虚线关联到S33_root。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S33",
        "S33_root",
        "S33_A",
        "S33_B",
        "S33_C",
        "D33"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，S33_B和S33_C之间的连接好像有问题。执行器控制器应该是最终消费数据的，但现在看起来S33_B直接指向S33_C，这个方向对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S33_B",
        "S33_C"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "方向是对的，数据流从左到右：边缘节点→边缘Broker→云端Broker→控制器。控制器接收云端下发的控制指令或遥测数据。需要调整什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S33_root",
        "S33_A",
        "S33_B",
        "S33_C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "方向没问题，但我刚才看错了——S33_B的节点类型标成了和S33_A一样的MQTT Broker，这个是对的。不过确认一下，S33_C是ActuatorController，不是Broker对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S33_C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，S33_C是IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController，负责驱动工业执行器。四个节点类型分别是：EdgeNode、MQTT Broker、MQTT Broker、ActuatorController。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S33_root",
        "S33_A",
        "S33_B",
        "S33_C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后确认一下整体布局：子图用TB方向，D33放在外面通过虚线指向S33_root。这样从外部看，遥测流定义依赖具体的边缘节点实现。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D33",
        "S33_root",
        "S33"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。子图S33内部是自上而下的链式结构，D33用虚线边框，通过虚线连接到S33_root。整个工业遥测流架构清晰展示了从边缘到云端再到执行器的完整数据通路。",
